The '''Yag'Dhul Embassy''' was the representative body of [[Givin/Legends|Givin]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was connected to the [[Yag'Dhul Ambassadorial Landing Platform]] and was adjacent to the [[Ansion Embassy]].

